{"data":[{"date":"07:28 09/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/1/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00eda Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn.</h2><h2>Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, vi\u1ec7c Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Courtois</span> tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Kovacic ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y. V\u00ec v\u1eady, d\u00f9 Kovacic c\u00f3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ea5y th\u00ec The Blues c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch g\u00ec gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/CHINH-THUC-Tien-ve-Kovacic-gia-nhap-Chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc trao cho Kovacic m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh N&rsquo;golo Kante v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Jorginho \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League n\u0103m nay b\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Huddersfield. V\u00e0 HLV Sarri k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea3 hai t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 Kovacic v\u00e0 Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ra m\u1eaft th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Kepa. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi ra t\u1edbi 72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Bilbao nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf Courtois.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea l\u1ed7 n\u1eb7ng v\u1edbi v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i Courtois - Kovacic</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Chelsea ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n Kovacic t\u1eeb Real l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Courtois v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Kovacic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m nay Kovacic m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 24 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2015 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i Chelsea s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Kovacic n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Real trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\">Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194065.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2156","checkdouble":"194070"},{"date":"07:13 09/08","title":"CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/clb-thai-son-nam-lap-ky-tich-o-giai-vo-dich-futsal-chau-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sanchez cho r\u1eb1ng Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Arturo Vidal \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.</h2><h2>Sanchez mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, HLV Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Harry Maguire, Jerome Boateng v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sanchez y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam si\u00eau sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sanchez y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam si\u00eau sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/sanchez-yeu-cau-mu-chieu-mo-them-sieu-sao.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Alexis Sanchez mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Sanchez cho r\u1eb1ng Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i k\u00edch n\u1ed5 th\u00eam \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d. Theo ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Arturo Vidal l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 MU c\u1ea7n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u1ede Man United, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Barcelona m\u1edbi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Vidal, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Chile.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTheo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 t\u00f4i quan s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, Fred l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n lao l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n d\u00e2ng cao. V\u00e0 theo t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap \u00edch nhi\u1ec1u cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Sanchez t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Old Trafford sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Sanchez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Premier League n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh. Khi b\u1ea1n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00ec b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong 6 th\u00e1ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0m quen c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n mang \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00ec c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-barca-thay-the-luke-shaw-172-194037.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao Barca thay th\u1ebf Luke Shaw</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-jerome-boateng-khong-phai-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-mu-172-194042.html\">V\u00ec sao Jerome Boateng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi MU?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2155","checkdouble":"194071"},{"date":"08:03 09/08","title":"Sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real th\u1ec1 ch\u1ebft \u201cchi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d c\u00f9ng Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/keylor-navas-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Keylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 31 tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0 ch\u1ebft ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c trong cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh Thibaut Courtois.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nReal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Courtois</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois. Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, Courtois s\u1ebd sang ch\u01a1i cho Real theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro. \u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, Los Blancos s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m. Sau bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c, Courtois s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (9/8) t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Keylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Keylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/keylor-navas-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Keylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNavas quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Courtois c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Real nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua l\u00e0 Keylor Navas nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Los Blancos mu\u1ed1n thay tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9 l\u00ean su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia nh\u1eadp Real t\u1eeb Levante n\u0103m 2014, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n Navas \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft t\u1ed1t. Anh c\u00f9ng B\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u00e0 1 La Liga c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Keylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nghi\u00eam t\u00fac r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. N\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i th\u00e0 ch\u1ebft c\u00f2n h\u01a1n&rdquo;, Navas n\u00f3i tr\u00ean ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Onda Cero.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\">Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-chi-tiet-hop-dong-courtois-sap-ky-voi-real-madrid-172-194030.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Courtois s\u1eafp k\u00fd v\u1edbi Real Madrid?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/luka-modric-tinh-roi-real-sang-inter-milan-180-193950.html\">V\u00ec &ldquo;mi\u1ebfng b\u00e1nh&rdquo; b\u00e9o b\u1edf n\u00e0y, Modric t\u00ednh b\u1ecf Real sang Inter</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-tu-choi-tro-lai-chelsea-quyet-tam-den-real-bang-duoc-172-193892.html\">Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2154","checkdouble":"194072"},{"date":"08:22 09/08","title":"Chi ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng, t\u1ea1i sao Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Rugani?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/juventus-khong-muon-ban-daniel-rugani-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniele Rugani cho Chelsea. H\u1ecd quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00f9 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rugani</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a n\u00e0y thay cho \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Antonio Conte, HLV Maurizio Sarri quy\u1ebft th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. Sau khi mang v\u1ec1 Jorginho t\u1eeb Napoli, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia quy\u1ebft t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Daniele Rugani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Rugani t\u1eebng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng Sarri 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2013/14 v\u00e0 2014/15 t\u1ea1i Empoli. Sau \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus song su\u1ed1t 3 n\u0103m qua v\u1eabn ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniele Rugani cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniele Rugani cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/juventus-khong-muon-ban-daniel-rugani-cho-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rugani n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAi c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Juventus s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 Chelsea trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Rugani.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Leonardo Bonucci t\u1eeb AC Milan, Juventus kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniele Rugani cho Chelsea. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a The Blues l\u1edbn t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn gi\u1eef v\u1eefng l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chi dam mua Rugani\" title=\"Arsenal chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Rugani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Chelsea-mua-Daniele-Rugani-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniele Rugani cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Juventus kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Rugani, h\u1ecd h\u00e9t m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi tr\u1ea3&rdquo;, Torchia n\u00f3i v\u1edbi RMC Sport. &ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd y\u00eau c\u1ea7u chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. L\u1eafng nghe m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i Turin. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1edbn, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng Juventus \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Rugani c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\">Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mateo-kovacic-sap-den-chelsea-172-194055.html\">Ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ea5t Courtois, Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-athletic-bilbao-xac-nhan-kepa-arrizabalaga-sap-den-chelsea-172-194052.html\">N\u00f3ng: Athletic Bilbao x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Kepa Arrizabalaga s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/david-luiz-ung-ho-chelsea-mua-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194049.html\">Chelsea chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c mua Kepa, David Luiz n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2153","checkdouble":"194073"},{"date":"08:36 09/08","title":"H\u1ecdc Mourinho, Sanchez y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam si\u00eau sao","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/sanchez-yeu-cau-mu-chieu-mo-them-sieu-sao.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sanchez cho r\u1eb1ng Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Arturo Vidal \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.</h2><h2>Sanchez mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, HLV Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Harry Maguire, Jerome Boateng v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sanchez y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam si\u00eau sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sanchez y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam si\u00eau sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/sanchez-yeu-cau-mu-chieu-mo-them-sieu-sao.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Alexis Sanchez mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Sanchez cho r\u1eb1ng Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i k\u00edch n\u1ed5 th\u00eam \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d. Theo ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Arturo Vidal l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 MU c\u1ea7n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u1ede Man United, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Barcelona m\u1edbi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Vidal, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Chile.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTheo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 t\u00f4i quan s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, Fred l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n lao l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n d\u00e2ng cao. V\u00e0 theo t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap \u00edch nhi\u1ec1u cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Sanchez t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Old Trafford sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Sanchez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Premier League n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh. Khi b\u1ea1n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00ec b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong 6 th\u00e1ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0m quen c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n mang \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00ec c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-barca-thay-the-luke-shaw-172-194037.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao Barca thay th\u1ebf Luke Shaw</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-jerome-boateng-khong-phai-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-mu-172-194042.html\">V\u00ec sao Jerome Boateng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi MU?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2152","checkdouble":"194074"},{"date":"08:44 09/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y song G\u0110 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Witthaya Laohakul v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"u23 thai lan\" title=\"u23 th\u00e1i lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i k\u00ec v\u1ecdng \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1eebng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD nh\u1edd vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &lsquo;Messi Th\u00e1i&rsquo;, Chanathip Songkrasin.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Trong th\u1eddi gian qua, \u0111\u1ed9i U23 c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u0129 thu\u1eadt L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT), \u00f4ng Witthaya Laohakul v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf ASIAD n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ASIAD 2014, v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u00edt th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m to\u00e0n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23. T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Worrawoot Srimaka n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Olympic Uzbekistan, Olympic Qatar v\u00e0 Olympic Bangladesh. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Olympic Qatar v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\">U23 Th\u00e1i Lan lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Myanmar</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Alpine Cup 2018, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/trong-khi-viet-nam-thang-hoa-u23-thai-lan-tiep-tuc-thua-tui-nhuc-tai-myanmar-168-193796.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/trong-khi-viet-nam-thang-hoa-u23-thai-lan-tiep-tuc-thua-tui-nhuc-tai-myanmar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/trong-khi-viet-nam-thang-hoa-u23-thai-lan-tiep-tuc-thua-tui-nhuc-tai-myanmar-168-193796.html\">U23 Th\u00e1i  Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua t\u1ee7i nh\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Myanmar</span><br>\r\nU23 Th\u00e1i Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Alpine Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Myanmar.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2151","checkdouble":"194075"},{"date":"08:36 09/08","title":"Barca c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/23/barca-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-mignolet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Simon Mignolet, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi Barca.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mignolet \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Simon Mignolet th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 cho Rakirus. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool mua Alisson t\u1eeb Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, The Kop b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mua anh v\u1ec1 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Barca, Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Simon Mignolet h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Barca, Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Simon Mignolet h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/20/Vuot-mat-Barca,-Napoli-muon-mua-Simon-Mignolet-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Mignolet mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMignolet l\u00fac n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Liverpool, sau Karius v\u00e0 Alisson. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. \u0110\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00e0i d\u00e0i \u1edf Anfield, c\u1ef1u sao Sunderland \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Mignolet ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, Liverpool c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. The Kop mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Napoli quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Simon Mignolet</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-chi-11-trieu-bang-mua-cai-ten-khong-the-ngo-toi-cua-liverpool-180-192432.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Barca h\u1ecfi mua Simon Mignolet</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 thay th\u1ebf Jasper Cillessen, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i do kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu thanh Mignolet co kha nang can pha phat den rat tot.\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Mignolet c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/16/barca-chi-11-trieu-bang-mua-cai-ten-khong-the-ngo-toi-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Mignolet&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Simon Mignolet, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i t\u1edbi Italia, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia c\u00f2n h\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c cho ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Napoli \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Mignolet y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Liverpool song c\u1ef1u sao Sunderland v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2150","checkdouble":"194076"},{"date":"08:48 09/08","title":"PSG \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/psg-dam-phan-chieu-mo-boateng.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 38 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern Munich ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Jerome Boateng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 38 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 38 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/psg-dam-phan-chieu-mo-boateng.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U v\u00ec Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111\u00f2i 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 M.U chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Bild c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/boateng-tu-choi-mu-vi-mourinho-172-194013.html\" target=\"_blank\">Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU</span>, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng HLV Jose Mourinho. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i cho r\u1eb1ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh \u1edf Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBoateng \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern Munich, song anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Boateng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 38 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern Munich ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern chi ban Boateng voi gia 50 trieu bang\" title=\"Bayern ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/boateng-tu-choi-mu-vi-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Boateng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 PSG d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra c\u00f2n k\u00e9m 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng so v\u1edbi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Bayern, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Boateng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd chi \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Boateng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n\u00a0c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Ngo\u00e0i trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Bayern, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed c\u00f2n nh\u1eafm Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2149","checkdouble":"194077"},{"date":"08:41 09/08","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb Real Madrid t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/sao-tre-real-madrid-tu-tin-se-bung-no-mua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Julen Lopetegui. Sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Real Madrid t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ceballos kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDani Ceballos chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid t\u1eeb Real Betis v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 18 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2017. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 4 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i La Liga. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb HLV Zinedine Zidane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin Ceballos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Zidane v\u00e0 Julen Lopetegui l\u00ean thay, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n. Ceballos xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Real t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Julen Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Julen Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Dani-Ceballos.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nT\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u00ean k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Ceballos cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo;, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng. S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin chi\u1ebfm 80% b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a HLV c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Ch\u00ednh Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 cho t\u00f4i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi Real, Ceballos \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Real Betis. Ngo\u00e0i 1 m\u00f9a ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 2, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 Andalusia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 64 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i La Liga 2 m\u00f9a 2015/16 v\u00e0 2016/17.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-khong-muon-so-sanh-bale-va-ronaldo-180-194028.html\">HLV Real kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n so s\u00e1nh Bale v\u00e0 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-truoc-mua-201819-dau-roi-nhung-ke-khoc-muon-180-194020.html\">Real th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 Juventus v\u00e0 Roma: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/keylor-navas-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-real-madrid-180-194072.html\">Sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real th\u1ec1 ch\u1ebft &ldquo;chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo; c\u00f9ng Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\">Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2148","checkdouble":"194078"},{"date":"23:35 08/08","title":"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A CHINH TH\u1ee8C \u0111\u1ed5i sang logo m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu si\u00eau sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A m\u00f9a n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n khi chia tay logo c\u0169 sang th\u00e0nh m\u1eabu m\u1edbi mang h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean Serie A nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn ngh\u0129. L\u00e0n s\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh khi Serie A h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau Premier League v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00e1c CLB b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo nh\u1eb1m t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Serie A c\u0169ng l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c g\u00f3i ba n\u0103m gi\u1ed1ng Premier League. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo m\u1edbi theo h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n, nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o ch\u1eef \"A\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Serie A c\u0169ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u00e1c trang m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i m\u1edbi tr\u00ean Facebook, Instagram v\u00e0 Twitter, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t t\u00ean \"SerieA\". Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng h\u01a1n h\u01a1n 1.2 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i logo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Serie A t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \"xu\u1ed1ng gi\u00e1\". Ch\u1eef A trong logo m\u1edbi c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \"Appassionante, Avvincente, Adrenalinica\" - t\u1ea1m d\u1ecbch \"th\u00fa v\u1ecb, h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, b\u01a1m Adrenaline\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Logo cu cua Serie A.\" title=\"Logo c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Serie A.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/serie-a-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Logo c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Serie A.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBan \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Serie A k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng logo m\u1edbi b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb \"khao kh\u00e1t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u00ednh trung t\u00e2m cho ch\u1eef A\", c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \"m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta\". Vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i logo Serie A c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Italia nh\u01b0 Coppa Italia, Si\u00eau C\u00fap Italia v\u00e0 Primavera.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"M\u1ed9t c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn m\u1edbi, t\u1ea1o ra t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c quan, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n g\u1ed3m l\u00e1 c\u1edd Italia, m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u1eef A, t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi TIM\" - Tr\u00edch t\u1eeb th\u00f4ng c\u00e1o b\u00e1o ch\u00ed.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Serie A 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-nhan-xet-cristiano-ronaldo-den-serie-a-176-193919.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0ng kim c\u1ee7a Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao-176-193834.html\">M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf Juventus kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/liverpool-vs-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193724.html\">Liverpool 5-0 Napoli: The Klopp h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Serie A trong ng\u00e0y Alisson ra m\u1eaft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-dong-y-o-lai-serie-a-176-192603.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-khi-sao-serie-a-la-mieng-pizza-trong-mat-cac-dai-gia-nha-172-192560.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Khi sao Serie A l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng pizza trong m\u1eaft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia NHA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/sieu-sao-ronaldo-giup-juventus-pha-ky-luc-tren-youtube-188-192551.html\">Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo gi\u00fap Juventus ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c tr\u00ean YouTube</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2147","checkdouble":"194058"},{"date":"00:05 09/08","title":"Paul Scholes ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man Utd m\u00f9a n\u00e0y k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/paul-scholes-che-doi-hinh-man-utd-mua-nay-kem-chat-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Paul Scholes kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Manchester United, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 HLV Jose Mourinho nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Paul Scholes ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man Utd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Jose Mourinho, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Man Utd hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Wayne Rooney cho r\u1eb1ng Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Scholes che doi hinh Man Utd mua nay kem chat luong.\" title=\"Paul Scholes ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man Utd m\u00f9a n\u00e0y k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/paul-scholes-che-doi-hinh-man-utd-mua-nay-kem-chat-luong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Paul Scholes ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man Utd m\u00f9a n\u00e0y k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp h\u01a1n, Paul Scholes ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man Utd kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7: &quot;Khi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o Man City hay Liverpool, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Man Utd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ed1t&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Man Utd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Man City. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i th\u00ec ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft r\u1ed3i, c\u00f2n Man Utd th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng ai bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn. Hy v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 t\u00f4i sai nh\u01b0ng Man Utd kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, HLV Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gi\u00fap Man Utd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a &quot;qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot; b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n khi ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ec1u cao c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Scholes cung cho rang Jose Mourinho co nguy co bi sa thai trong mua nay.\" title=\"Paul Scholes c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i trong m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/mourinho-13.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Paul Scholes c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i trong m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i \u1edf Anh \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Jose Mourinho l\u00e0 HLV c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Paul Scholes c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 Mourinho: &quot;Kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i. N\u1ebfu Man Utd ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng mang t\u00ednh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Man Utd m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-88-man-utd-can-them-2-tan-binh-184-194054.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 8/8: Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-pogba-co-the-da-trung-ve-172-194003.html\">Mourinho: Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1... trung v\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/mu-may-nhat-liverpool-xui-nhat-ngoai-hang-anh-mua-truoc-188-193943.html\">M.U may nh\u1ea5t, Liverpool xui nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-marcus-rashford-mang-ao-so-10-cua-man-utd-172-193910.html\">Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-man-utd-chinh-thuc-tim-ra-tan-chu-nhan-cho-ao-so-10-172-193824.html\">N\u00f3ng! Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u00ecm ra t\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n cho \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hang-hot-world-cup-tiep-tuc-tha-thinh-man-utd-172-193822.html\">H\u00e0ng hot World Cup ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh Man Utd</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2146","checkdouble":"194059"},{"date":"00:37 09/08","title":"Sao HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/sao-hagl-noi-gi-khi-bi-loai-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 71.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2>Kepa gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Bilbao \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 7 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 71.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-athletic-bilbao-xac-nhan-kepa-arrizabalaga-sap-den-chelsea-172-194052.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kepa \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge</span> \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho Thibaut Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Premier League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u00e0 Premier League. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00f4i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Chelsea n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Kepa</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge khi Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i quay l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Sarri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Kepa ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. D\u1eabu sao, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo l\u1eafng khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 Caballero \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Marina Granovskaia kh\u00e1 h\u00e2n hoan v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Chelsea v\u1eeba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cKepa l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea7n kh\u00edch khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Kepa \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eeba k\u00fd v\u1edbi Kepa th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mateo-kovacic-sap-den-chelsea-172-194055.html\">Ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ea5t Courtois, Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/david-luiz-ung-ho-chelsea-mua-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194049.html\">Chelsea chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c mua Kepa, David Luiz n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2145","checkdouble":"194060"},{"date":"05:53 09/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 9/8: Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-sang-ngay-98-chelsea-lap-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 9/8.</h2><h2>Everton l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Everton \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng t\u1ea1i Barca hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Andre Gomes. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Everton c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Andre Gomes thay v\u00ec mua \u0111\u1ee9t nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa v\u1edbi ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa\" title=\"Kepa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng 9/8: Kepa ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kepa gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho Courtois. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 The Blues ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho Athletic Bilbao l\u00e0 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, t\u1ee9c kho\u1ea3ng 72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Kepa \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua con s\u1ed1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Alisson \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c l\u1eadp c\u0169ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Schalke ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn sao Tottenham</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Rose \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Schalke thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 Bundesliga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y 31/8 v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho Schalke trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Spurs.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Boateng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Sky Sports \u0111\u01b0a tin HLV Jose Mourinho mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i trong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t giao k\u00e8o mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Man United b\u1ecb h\u1edb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Vida</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Evening Standard cho bi\u1ebft Arsenal \u0111ang quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 n\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng hay kh\u00f4ng. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Danny Welbeck t\u1edbi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 nh\u1eb1m gi\u1ea3m s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda Besiktas ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia. Vida \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mong mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-88-man-utd-can-them-2-tan-binh-184-194054.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 8/8: Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-88-pogba-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu-184-193992.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 8/8: Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2144","checkdouble":"194063"},{"date":"06:11 09/08","title":"C\u1ef1u sao Liverpool d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Lovren t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/4/lovren-nhm-ung-ho-toi-nhieu-hon-modric-va-kovacic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Dirk Kuyt kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trung v\u1ec7 Lovren \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Liverpool m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Kuyt \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Lovren</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Lovren trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m cho nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1ea1i Anfield. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi gi\u00fap Liverpool l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, Lovren c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia v\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/lovren-moi-nguoi-can-nhan-ra-chung-toi-la-nhung-nguoi-gioi-nhat-421-191045.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lovren \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u sao Liverpool d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Lovren t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u sao Liverpool d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Lovren t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/4/lovren-nhm-ung-ho-toi-nhieu-hon-modric-va-kovacic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kuyt d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Lovren s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Kuyt tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V Liverpool s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/dejan-lovren-44909.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lovren</span> \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cLovren l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch khi xem Croatia thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup. H\u1ecd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 gi\u00e2y. Croatia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Croatia r\u1ed3i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Kuyt d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Liverpool s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kuyt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Feyenoord gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan m\u00f9a 2016/17. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau g\u1ea7n 2 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 Kuyt tin r\u1eb1ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Liverpool ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t Premier League khi \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u00eau kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh tay \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cV\u1edbi Feyenoord, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u sau 18 n\u0103m. T\u00f4i tin Liverpool s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 sau 29 n\u0103m v\u00e0 Lovren s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 Van Dijk s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chi-co-bong-dang-cua-nha-vo-dich-sau-khi-chieu-mo-alisson-172-194000.html\">Liverpool ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-thua-nhan-liverpool-chot-so-chuyen-nhuong-172-193996.html\">Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Liverpool ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2143","checkdouble":"194064"},{"date":"06:33 09/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea k\u00edch n\u1ed5 \"bom t\u1ea5n\" th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 71.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2>Kepa gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Bilbao \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 7 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 71.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-athletic-bilbao-xac-nhan-kepa-arrizabalaga-sap-den-chelsea-172-194052.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kepa \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge</span> \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho Thibaut Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Premier League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u00e0 Premier League. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00f4i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Chelsea n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Kepa</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge khi Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i quay l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Sarri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Kepa ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. D\u1eabu sao, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo l\u1eafng khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 Caballero \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Marina Granovskaia kh\u00e1 h\u00e2n hoan v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Chelsea v\u1eeba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cKepa l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea7n kh\u00edch khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Kepa \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eeba k\u00fd v\u1edbi Kepa th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mateo-kovacic-sap-den-chelsea-172-194055.html\">Ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ea5t Courtois, Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/david-luiz-ung-ho-chelsea-mua-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194049.html\">Chelsea chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c mua Kepa, David Luiz n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2142","checkdouble":"194065"}]}